beforeMove() - Method in class jade.core.Agent
This empty placeholder shall be overridden by user defined agents to execute some actions before the original agent instance on the source container is stopped (e.g. releasing local resources such as a GUI).
IMPORTANT: At this point, it is ensured that the move process is successful and that a moved agent instance has been created on the destination container Therefore setting the value of a class field in this method will have no impact on the moved agent instance.
